message:
You had to get up pretty early in the morning to cash in on yesterday's GTC Gitcoin low of $1.72, up 48¢ to $2.20 for a short spurt this morning!
#ThirdGenCrypto
Tip: I wait until everyone's done buying for the day for prices to come down, and then buy at the end of the day. Early morning buyers offer selling opportunities.
It's not 100% but I keep it in the portfolio of strategies for when it's handy (sell when everyone's trading / buy when the market's quiet and no one's buying or looking)
